0.9.name: wordpress/wd3k-give-feedback
0.9.description:
Creates "Give Feedback" button in the right bottom corner of the post page. After click, redirects user to the comment box. This technique helps you to increase the number of user feedback

Uses jQuery for setting transparency when you move your mouse over the button (animated).
